FBIS3-57039 "drsov015_r_94005" FBIS-SOV-94-015 Document Type:Daily Report 25 Jan 1994 Azerbaijan INTERFAX Reports Attack on Goradiz LD2301230194 Moscow Ostankino Television First Channel Network in Russian 2200 GMT 23 Jan 94 LD2301230194 Moscow Ostankino Television First Channel Network Language: Russian Article Type:BFN [From the "Novosti" newscast] [Text] According to an Interfax report from Baku, Armenian formations are trying to mount an offensive on Goradiz, a strategically important railway station located near the Azeri- Iranian frontier. According to the same source, combat Armenian Army helicopters mounted a rocket strike on the population centers of Terterskiy Rayon of Azerbaijan.
